snippet.title: Syntherapy - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
If an AI were sentient, how would you know if they were malfunctioning, or experiencing a mental health problem? In Syntherapy, it’s your job to help ‘Willow’, an advanced experimental AI, find out before those funding the project shut them down.

Developer: Crowned Daemon Studios
Publisher: V Publishing

Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qHJaJNLmVXU

Syntherapy on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1077470/Syntherapy/
